[SN]TITLE[SN]
Fire crews tackle grass blaze on Penrhys mountain

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Crews are tackling a grass fire on Penrhys mountain, Rhondda Cynon Taff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It covers an area of about 20 hectares (50 acres) and five engines are at the scene.
A spokeswoman for South Wales Fire and Rescue Service said there is not currently a risk to nearby houses.
But she added an area is "well alight".
